title: UTC Women's Basketball Teams Facing Daunting Schedule This Season
text: Chattanooga-(WDEF) Practice got underway this weekend for the UTC's women's basketball team. Lot of high hopes for the Mocs this year and why not. They return nine players from a SoCon champion team that went 29-4 last year. But UTC faces a daunting non-conference schedule this year with the Lady Vols, Stanford, and U-Conn.Said guard Alicia Payne, "We're really excited to play. We're really ready to start off the season that way because it will give us a lot of experience. Teach us a lot of things. I think it will help us later on." Said head coach Jim Foster-"We make no secret that we would like to win some games in the NCAA Tournament. We'd like to advance. And what we do is schedule accordingly."
